<b><font class="print-title">Ninja Patch March 30th...</font></b><br /><br />
<font class="print-sub">Articles / EverQuest Patches<br />
<b>Date:</b> Mar 30, 2004 - 10:09 PM</font>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>
<font class="print-normal">With no notice really, it was announced the server's would be brought down in 15 mins. Now we're seeing the following that was addressed. Seems that the patch was for pink icon borders and mobs that were spawning under the world... both good fixes!<br>
<br>
-Wandering monsters should no longer have collision issues which cause them to vanish.<br>
-Server latency should be improved.<br>
-Due to a lack of popularity, we will be removing the pink border from spell icons. (what's wrong with pink?)<br /><br />
<br />
</font>
</td></tr>
